race.comment: SMART ENERGY (3) went back-to-back to end last campaign and looks in good order this time in work judging by his recent trials. Carbery reunites with the gelding and he maps for a lovely run first-up today. Might be better over further, though this looks a very winnable race for him on resumption. ZORBRIST (4) resumed here and has placed first-up in the past. His trial coming in was sound and if he can pick up from where he left off last campaign then he'll be right in the finish. MANTUA (1) gets barrier 1 and CJP in the saddle as he steps back out to 1200m today. Sure to go close. RANYX (6) is better than we saw last time out and can bounce back.
